Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Trči*š brže od mene. (You're running faster than me.)
2. Vidim da *trči*š svaki dan ujutru. (I see that you run every morning.)
3. Ne bi trebalo da *trči*š na prazan stomak. (You shouldn't run on an empty stomach.)
4. Rekao sam joj da *trči* što brže može. (I told her to run as fast as she could.)
5. Često *trči*š maratone, zar ne? (You often run marathons, don't you?)
6. Sinoć sam *trčao* pet kilometara. (Last night I ran five kilometers.)
7. Ako *trčiš* svaki dan, trebalo bi da budeš u dobroj formi. (If you run every day, you should be in good shape.)
8. *Trčaćemo* sutra ujutru zajedno. (We'll run together tomorrow morning.)
9. Molim vas da *trčite* u suprotnom pravcu. (Please run in the opposite direction.)
10. Koliko brzo možeš *trčati* na kratke staze? (How fast can you run short distances?)

I hope this helps!